replies.body:
> don&#x27;t give players tools to punish their own team mates. 

So then you agree that the report and punishment system is a great idea! Flaming gets reported and then flamers get chat restricted, so the tool that punishes your teammates (chat) is taken away. I'm so happy we agree that toxic players should have their chat rights removed so they stop punishing their teammates with their toxicity.

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
